{"tid":1181200,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"因與近期超英大片劇情雷同  《X戰警：黑鳳凰》花千萬重拍","createTime":"2019-06-01T12:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T15:49:57.000Z","uid":49391,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"412d60f89bb5b7bd51e859bd08723dacd441b06e","tid":1181200,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"此前有消息稱，《X戰警：黑鳳凰》的補拍工作，花費近1000萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n  近日，《X戰警：黑鳳凰》的主演詹姆斯&bull;麥卡沃伊在接受采訪時說，先前電影重拍是因為結局和另外一部超級英雄電影情節撞車。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeiwiKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeiwiKj.jpg&h=2cc6abb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《X戰警：黑鳳凰》的上映日期，從去年11月一直拖到了今年6月6日。因為首輪試映之後，內部決定進行一些補拍，但是主演都有各自的片約在身，協調時間是個很困難的問題。所以時間一拖再拖，就從去年拖到了今年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42yz0XF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42yz0XF.jpg&h=6b043c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此前對於此次補拍事宜，導演西蒙&bull;金伯格曾經做出過回應，內部決定重拍電影的第三幕，將原本的太空大戰改為火車上的戰斗場景。這個決定剛公開時，大量粉絲表示不滿，認為這種改動是不合理的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0Uvzh0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0Uvzh0.jpg&h=5d32cd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近期正值《X戰警：黑鳳凰》宣傳期，主演詹姆斯&bull;麥卡沃伊提起了這個問題，他說：&ldquo;結局真的改變了很多，而且必須改變，因為影片與不久之前發行的另一部超級英雄電影情節，產生了重疊和相似。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7GhYKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7GhYKF.jpg&h=9e7ca876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時接受采訪的邁克爾&bull;法斯賓德開玩笑說：&ldquo;在片場有他們的間諜，大抵偷走了我們的想法。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  蘇菲&bull;特納說：&ldquo;你看完前兩幕，再看第三幕確實沒有凝聚力。我們返回片場，幾乎重拍了全部第三幕，這是一個很好的決定。對我來說，第三幕是電影的最佳部分。&rdquo;此次參與拍攝的傑西卡&bull;查斯坦也表示，她扮演的角色，甚至因為重拍在故事上都發生了變化。"},{"pid":"2e5a0b7e8616902887ce3657103db6475b4b0a18","tid":1181200,"uid":49391,"like":218,"dislike":16,"score":202,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"邊套?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點雷同法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計我話根本唔需要重拍,反正d人成日話呢類英雄片無劇情/劇情一鳩樣"},{"pid":"f6a729f667e7e99e780be027bbc3d4e4009ed5f4","tid":1181200,"uid":7943,"like":267,"dislike":3,"score":264,"quote":{"pid":"2e5a0b7e8616902887ce3657103db6475b4b0a18","tid":1181200,"uid":49391,"like":218,"dislike":16,"score":202,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"邊套?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點雷同法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計我話根本唔需要重拍,反正d人成日話呢類英雄片無劇情/劇情一鳩樣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"Captain marvel? <br />\n根本唔洗重拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拍得好過佢咪得"},{"pid":"817ef093817ea437f40802a0691b246fb8a0c657","tid":1181200,"uid":119223,"like":151,"dislike":12,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會係DC套 沙贊掂硬!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平分Phoenix Force變鳳凰戰隊?"},{"pid":"e92137db9b6f3772dce867fd140b8c6d56f2e416","tid":1181200,"uid":36065,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"九成係全部人消失晒"},{"pid":"4661bc014c66bd1fdb08d3f954a11d264229b86f","tid":1181200,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"Superman"},{"pid":"e871f675cd9db567f93e01f43bd9899bd6d1372e","tid":1181200,"uid":37596,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"e92137db9b6f3772dce867fd140b8c6d56f2e416","tid":1181200,"uid":36065,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"九成係全部人消失晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce61bebd619ad4bba0acf72b21e42f19c98ba51","tid":1181200,"uid":149494,"like":7,"dislike":178,"score":-171,"quote":{"pid":"f6a729f667e7e99e780be027bbc3d4e4009ed5f4","tid":1181200,"uid":7943,"like":267,"dislike"